{"tid":1463892,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟爬山，各自努力，我地要做嘅係互相幫手，唔係互相指責","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:13:15.000Z","uid":98507,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e615aadf5a4b1dca25e4d1328f7a9e3571b8b4b8","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:59:59.000Z","msg":"記唔記得七一？<br />\n當時衝立法會好多人話有鬼，唔好衝<br />\n但最後民意都係冇乜點失去<br />\n點解？唔係因為衝立法會係一件冇問題嘅事<br />\n唔係因為黑警做得太柒<br />\n而係衝完之後<br />\n好多人都衝出黎幫呢班手足解釋，去搶道德高地<br />\n點解反而今時今日，做唔到呢樣野？<br />\n阻遊客上機<br />\n好嘅係傷到政府，唔好嘅係傷到遊客<br />\n抗爭係冇可能魚同熊掌兼得，請你地明白呢個道理<br />\n損失係一定有，你望下有幾多手足被補，有幾多人以死明志？<br />\n但唔代表我地要接受損失<br />\n相反我地要做野減低損失<br />\n麻煩大家出盡奶力去幫手足搶高地，唔好互相指責"},{"pid":"b44d64afb8cc3c353e2d805d4225b21359f3e232","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:06:29.000Z","msg":"如果真係驚遊客反感，驚失去外國勢力<br />\n有口才嘅手足幫手向佢地解釋<br />\n再唔係咪好似稅局咁道歉<br />\n呢d野我地都唔係第一次做<br />\n亡羊就要補牢，唔好再比情緒影響發洩左出黎先<br />\n要諗對策呀"},{"pid":"52f6830c1989e024f684235b76c6ad5353ffa045","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b131be20758a941fd79a5ef032131758e76d20b7","tid":1463892,"uid":147782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64083bef7487c61401a35128114c29aa446bf9b4","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:14:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1945fa4ae095c7a9f9a311ae79fb1b19242bbed9","tid":