3:30:35.000Z","msg":"成日開post問割唔割<br />\n唔係口講一句唔割或者評完分就算<br />\n請大家一齊努力帶返好個風向<br />\n全力煲大公安事件"},{"pid":"0dd0e3ff4b24ae7a9f133986cb80b3bd16d9f5f8","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:42:15.000Z","msg":"我地係冇大台<br />\n所以唔同人都有唔同做法<br />\n咁先正正係兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n如果兄弟有咩做得唔好 跌低左<br />\n我地係應該扶返起佢<br />\n而唔係屌佢<br />\n不指責呀<br />\n唔好中政府陷阱<br />\n唔好內鬥<br />\n我知大家而家只係「檢討」緊<br />\n但檢討同時都要做好文宣<br />\n努力同人解釋<br />\n唔好任由佢地抹黑"},{"pid":"3d7804ccbe483ff6f954fceebcfeb4691478a88a","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa2bb0b5e7f97f228d51c7607f52e0541f28bc5","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:15:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86695029b8975ff096032ab03210955eb08dd626","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:17:30.000Z","msg":"我地仲有818遊行<br />\n而家再唔搶高地<br />\n到時人數好影響我地嘅後續嘅方向"},{"pid":"67347df01a87cacd1082b4f75afe76c0fd67ffd0","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388bdc3f5b497941cde74fbde86896e563a54f12","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7362e2ad4aa8b48f4ea264d68f735961c61dc5b","tid":1463892,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d059b8ffd15d07a60cf53567806446067b6f24b3